<<devactor '_actorname1'>> must be best friends with
<<devactor '_actorname2'>>.
</p>

<<link '(Continue)' 'QGRestrictionDone'>>
  <<set $qrestriction = setup.qres.BestFriends(_actorname1, _actorname2)>>
<</link>>



